import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IFeeTransactionEntry } from '../fee-transaction-entry.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-fee-transaction-entry-detail', templateUrl: './fee-transaction-entry-detail.component.html', }) export class FeeTransactionEntryDetailComponent implements OnInit { feeTransactionEntry: IFeeTransactionEntry | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ feeTransactionEntry }) => { this.feeTransactionEntry = feeTransactionEntry; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
